lead_paragraph: Arsene Wenger dismissed protests against him as more "disappointed love" than "real aggression" after disenchanted supporters held up banners calling for his resignation in the 1-0 victory over Norwich in the Premier League on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Wenger Says Arsenal Protesters Full of 'Disappointed Love'
headline.main: Wenger Says Arsenal Protesters Full of 'Disappointed Love'
